{"tid":2171751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女學生管有酒精食用醋曾被杜浩成大幅加重保釋條件　今高等法院減回警署報到至毎周一次","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T10:33:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"31421d5b3d6157158a357819119310ebd60bb617","tid":2171751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8569&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=cbfb3096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8569</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭<br />\n#張慧玲法官<br />\n#1118觀塘 #更改保釋條件<br />\n<br />\n梁(16)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：串謀意圖損害等而施用有害物品<br />\n（香港法例第212章侵害人身罪條例第23條 及第200章第159條(a)及(c)）<br />\n<br />\n被控於2019年11月18日，於香港意圖以異丙醇、乙醇及乙酸的混合物中釋放的氣體，使警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n更改保釋條件獲批<br />\n ✅更改獲批<br />\n ⁃ 警署報到次數減少：每星期一次（原本四次）<br />\n ⁃ 宵禁令：22:00-05:00（原本21:00-8:00）<br />\n<br />\n🟢原有條件<br />\n ⁃ 保釋金 $20000 <br />\n ⁃ 不得離港<br />\n ⁃ 交出旅遊證件<br />\n ⁃ 居住在報稱住址（更改住址須24小時前通知警方）"},{"pid":"c6d9eb02364e8cf0557b4be910f24f36b430b8a5","tid":2171751,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c30dc17fe65819216d3c26aa6faebeecd8aa593","tid":2171751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"上次提堂:兩中五生背囊被搜出酒精食用醋 杜浩成:需要加重保釋條件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2139263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2139263</a>"},{"pid":"2bba94a4579caa5557645290fc07c842eda9965a","tid":2171751,"uid":275243,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"onL9杜酷刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a